        <ol>
        
            <li>
                The Earth's rotation is gradually slowing.
            </li>
            <li>
                A year isn't exactly 365 days, and the Earth doesn't take 24 hours to rotate.
            </li>
            <li>
                70% of the Earth's surface is water, and only one third of its fresh water is frozen.
            </li>
            
